{"tid":1557842,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"焦土計劃：911燒山 官媒：911將會有反政府示威者發動恐襲","createTime":"2019-09-10T09:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T03:59:42.000Z","uid":274262,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"46cb9a3f820a51f38a86f5d90f7b72800e6f1ca7","tid":1557842,"uid":274262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5Y3gRL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5Y3gRL.jpg&h=20d3db17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前話燒郊野公園嗰班友話<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>911要死人</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日官媒China Daily嘅fb post:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5qsfSre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5qsfSre.jpg&h=e2614cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂，明眼人都知咩事啦，就算真係會做激進啲有咩可能會揀九一一嚟想打擊人權法案。<br />\n<br />\n我有理由相信係中共想用番1950年代打冧國民黨嗰招<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暗殺+抹黑</span></strong>，所以唔該各位要喺聽日之前做好外國文宣等工作，防止佢地E個陰招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. E個唔係搞分化，前線係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有勇有謀</span></strong>，唔撚會做埋E種損人不利己嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔郁，唯有靠你地，必要時請開多個post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b902e67b92b93714aaf00a1a583da0df2c7d25","tid":1557842,"uid":117968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0581894c564be4c64de15574eb83f4ccc2cc383b","tid":1557842,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ee5ec58c90fddac15d2c6235957f66a8723f85","tid":1557842,"uid":192212,